title._content: Four Mile Lake with Mt. Mcloughlin in the Background

description._content: Item Description: The photographer was standing on the edge of the dam near the head gates of the flume when this picture was taken. The lake is well stocked with trout and is a Mecca for Southern Oregon Fishermen.
